              'namespace': 'new_description',
              'value': '<p>We can all be a little sensitive sometimes, and that’s where our new ultra-gentle moisturizer comes in. Stressed-out skin is no match for this calming, hydrating, and non-irritating formula that reduces the appearance of redness over time. Plus, it’s full of good stuff—probiotics, colloidal oatmeal, cucumber & ginger—and 100% free of fragrance, alcohol, phthalates, sulfates & other irritants. Non-comedogenic & tested safe for sensitive skin..</p><p><span class="suitable">Suitable for:  </span>Best for sensitive skin</p>\n<div class="weight">1.7 fl oz/50 ml</div>\n<div class="left_side">\n<h4>94%</h4>\n<p>said that their skin felt soothed</p>\n<h4>91%</h4>\n<p>said that their skin looked less irritated</p>\n<h4>94%</h4>\n<p>said that the lotion was very calming</p>\n</div>\n<div class="questions">\n<div class="container">\n<h2>questions</h2>\n<div class="grid">\n<div class="grid__item large--two-thirds one-whole">\n<div class="grid question_list">\n<div class="grid__item one-half medium-down--one-whole question_item">\n<h5>Can I use Super Soothe even if my skin isn’t always sensitive?</h5>\n<p>Absolutely! The ultra-gentle, nourishing formula is ideal for those who experience signs of sensitive skin at any frequency—whether that’s all the time or only on occasion (i.e. when you’re traveling, stressed, or have a late night out).</p>\n</div>\n<div class="grid__item one-half medium-down--one-whole question_item">\n<h5>I can’t put any fragrance on my skin. Is Super Soothe fragrance free?</h5>\n<p>Super Soothe is 100% free of fragrance, alcohol, silicones, mineral oil, phthalates, PEGs, sulfates &amp; other irritants. Not only that, it’s non-comedogenic (so it won’t clog pores), hypoallergenic, and tested safe for sensitive skin.</p>\n</div>\n<div class="grid__item one-half medium-down--one-whole question_item">\n<h5>How do I know if I have sensitive skin? </h5>\n<p>Sensitive skin can be seen in a number of ways, including redness, rosacea, stinging, or itching. Those with sensitive skin also may have reactions when trying new products, especially those containing a fragrance. When in doubt, consult with a dermatologist to get the best recommendations for your skin. </p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class="benefits">\n<div class="one-whole">\n<div class="benefit_list"><h4>The benefits</h4><ul><li>Restores hydration levels and balance to distressed, irritated skin</li>\n<li>Hypoallergenic &amp; tested safe for sensitive skin</li>\n<li>Non-comedogenic, so it won’t clog pores</li>\n<li>100% free of fragrance, alcohol, silicones, mineral oil, phthalates, PEGs, sulfates &amp; other irritants</li>\n</ul></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class="use_it">\n<div class="container">\n<div class="grid">\n<div class="how_use">\n<div class="grid__item  medium-down--one-whole four-twelfths">\n<h2>How to use</h2>\n<p>Apply a dime-sized amount on clean skin, morning and night (or anytime your skin could use a little extra TLC). For best results, use with our Super Calm Gentle Milk Cleanser.</p>\n</div>\n<div class="grid__item medium-down--one-whole  eight-twelfths">\n<div class="use_img"><img src="//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1736/9637/files/us_pdp_howtouse_1760x968_moisturizer.jpg?59518" alt="Super Soothe - how to use"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class="inside">\n<div class="container">\n<div class="inside-content">\n<h2>WHAT’S INSIDE</h2>\n<div class="grid">\n<div class="grid__item one-third medium-large--two-quarters medium-down--one-whole">\n<ul class="ingredients-list"><li><strong>Colloidal oatmeal </strong>soothes and helps skin retain moisture</li>\n<li><strong>Cucumber</strong><span> </span>contains vitamin C and caffeic acid to help reduce the appearance of irritation</li>\n<li><strong>Ginger</strong><span> </span>evens the appearance of skin tone, improves elasticity, and has antioxidant properties that help prevent free radical damage</li><li><strong>Aloe</strong><span> </span>reduces the appearance of skin irritation &amp; inflammation</li>\n<li><strong>Probiotics</strong><span> </span>calm the look of inflammation &amp; redness, also helps skin lock in hydration and maintain balance</li>\n</ul>\n<a class="i_link">See the full ingredients list</a></div>\n<div class="grid__item one-third medium-large--two-quarters medium-down--one-whole">\n<div class="probiotic-strains">\n<h5>Probiotic strains</h5>\n<ul>\n<li class="BFL">\n<h5>Bifida Ferment Lysate</h5>\n<p>Hydrate and lock in moisture.</p>\n</li>\n</ul></div>\n<div class="free_from">\n<div class="free-icon_none"><img src="//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1736/9637/files/free-icon.png?v=1492333395" alt="Purifying Cleanser"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="grid__item one-third medium-large--two-quarters medium-down--one-whole">\n<div class="benefit_img"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1736/9637/files/us_pdp_benefits_950x925_moisturizer.jpg?59518" alt="Super Soothe - benefit"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class="full_ingredient">\n<p>Aqua/Water/Eau, Glycerin, C13-15 Alkane, Propanediol, Squalane, Cetearyl Olivate, Jojoba Esters, Hydrogenated Olive Oil, Sorbitan Olivate, Lactococcus Ferment Lysate, Sclerotium Gum, Butyrospermum Parkii (Shea) Butter, Opuntia Ficus-Indica Fruit Extract, Olea Europaea (Olive) Fruit Oil, Colloidal Oatmeal, Hydroxyacetophenone, 1,2-Hexanediol, Caprylyl Glycol, Helianthus Annuus (Sunflower) Seed Extract, Olea Europaea (Olive) Oil Unsaponifiables, Saccharomyces Cerevisiae Extract, Cucumis Sativus (Cucumber) Fruit Extract, Trisodium Ethylenediamine Disuccinate, Hordeum Vulgare Extract, Agastache Mexicana Flower/Leaf/Stem Extract, Zingiber Officinale (Ginger) Root Extract, Phenoxyethanol, Lactic Acid, Maltodextrin, Sodium Benzoate, Sodium Chloride, Potassium Sorbate, Aloe Barbadensis Leaf Juice, Tocopherol, Linum Usitatissimum (Linseed) Seed Extract.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class="result_data">\n<p>Restores balance to distressed, irritated skin on contact, and over time. Lightweight, fragrance-free formula leaves skin looking healthier and more hydrated.</p>\n\n<p><i>Based on self-assessment, 33 subjects during 2 weeks</i></p>\n\n</div>\n\n\n<div class="before_after"><img src="//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1736/9637/files/us_pdp_results_880x670_moisturizer.jpg?59518" alt="Super Soothe - results"></div>',
